properties.property: Four hunters who lived with their own feathery friend until death Their wish, to be reunited once again where they rest, to be remembered as one long after the end The hunter of North, who does not rest in shadow, seeks the bird with mighty claws and hunter's eye, to have him be near on the ground below His brother, the hunter of South, lays not near his sibling and not near the hunter of East, his wish to be with the bird he gifted with speech, long deceased Hunter of East was laid down in the line neither as the first or the last, the bird of beauty is the bird from his past The hunter of West went to rest with the hunters of the North and East, reunite him again with the bird which symbols peace Will you help these men find old friend once again?
